textAnnotations.description:
Bertram's face was grim. "You think it was the Smort,
don't you?" John gave a short langs. "I did," he
said; "but I'd better stop thinking that now.
Pericles is fitting with an identically similar one.
"₁
"So there you are, my dear." Peggy's eyes filled
with tear." It's so unfair, "she said.
